            "source": [
                "# \ud83e\udde0 Cultura Organizacional e o Impacto dos Benef\u00edcios\n",
                "\n",
                "Investiga\u00e7\u00e3o sobre o ROI (Retorno sobre Investimento) de pol\u00edticas de RH focadas em sa\u00fade mental tecnol\u00f3gica.\n",
                "\n",
                "---"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "id": "5ebd6f38",
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "import pandas as pd\n",
                "import numpy as np\n",
                "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
                "import seaborn as sns\n",
                "from collections import Counter\n",
                "\n",
                "# Configurar estilo\n",
                "sns.set_style(\"whitegrid\")\n",
                "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (14, 6)\n",
                "plt.rcParams['font.size'] = 10\n",
                "\n",
                "# Criar diretório de outputs\n",
                "import os\n",
                "os.makedirs('outputs', exist_ok=True)\n",
                "\n",
                "# Carregar dados\n",
                "df = pd.read_csv('data/processed/survey.csv')\n",
                "print(f\"Dataset carregado: {df.shape[0]} respostas, {df.shape[1]} variáveis\")\n",
                "print(f\"\\nColunas necessárias presentes: {all(col in df.columns for col in ['benefits', 'treatment', 'mental_health_consequence', 'phys_health_consequence', 'obs_consequence', 'leave'])}\")"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "id": "374402f4",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## \ud83d\udcca An\u00e1lise 1: O Peso dos Benef\u00edcios Formais\n",
                "\n",
                "**Objetivo:** Demonstrar como benef\u00edcios formais de sa\u00fade mental influenciam a busca por tratamento.\n",
                "\n",
                "**M\u00e9trica:** Taxa de ades\u00e3o a tratamento por categoria de benef\u00edcios (`benefits` \u00d7 `treatment`).\n",
                "\n",
                "---"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "id": "494d8679",
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# GRÁFICO 1: O Peso dos Benefícios\n",
                "# Análise: benefits (Yes / No / Don't know) × treatment\n",
                "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
                "sns.countplot(data=df, x='benefits', hue='treatment', palette='coolwarm', ax=ax)\n",
                "ax.set_title('O Peso dos Benefícios: Impacto na Busca por Tratamento', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
                "ax.set_xlabel('Empresa oferece benefícios formais de saúde mental?', fontsize=12)\n",
                "ax.set_ylabel('Número de Funcionários', fontsize=12)\n",
                "ax.legend(title='Busca Tratamento?', loc='upper right')\n",
                "ax.grid(axis='y', alpha=0.3)\n",
                "plt.tight_layout()\n",
                "plt.savefig('outputs/analise_1_beneficios.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')\n",
                "plt.show()"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "id": "conclusao1",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "### \u2705 Conclus\u00e3o \u2014 An\u00e1lise 1\n",
                "\n",
